title: Baby
lyrics:
When I see you
You see me too
But I don’t see you
No, I don’t see you
When you walk by

Head in the sky

I’m lost and confused

I feel overused



Baby, baby, lately



I wanted romance

I asked you to dance

Oh well you gave me the chance

Yeah you gave me the chance



Blue as the sky

I wanted to die

I wanted to die

Well I wanted to die



Baby, baby, lately



When we first met

I would not forget

Oh well I could not forget

The way that we met



I love being young

Dancing in the sun

Young people thrive

I’ve been hiding all the night



Baby, baby, lately
